<TITLE> Police arrest journalist Borhan Kabir for fraud </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Feb 8 (bdnews24.com)Police arrested journalist Syed Borhan Kabir Friday morning from his office in connection with a fraud case filed against him. Ramna police chief Doulat Akbar told bdnews24.com: "We arrested him at 10:30 am, showing a warrant of arrest issued by the court." Borhan is director and presenter of the BTV programme Poriprekkhit . He has previously worked on the Bangla language dailies Bhorer Kagoj and Ajker Kagoj . bdnews24.
